gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 126, Jazz 97
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Jazz, 126-97. Jayson Tatum led the way with 30 points, nine rebounds, and five assists for the Celtics, with Kristaps Porzingis adding 19 points and five rebounds in the victory. Lauri Markkanen tallied 17 points, five rebounds, and five assists for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Celtics improve to 27-7 in the regular season, while the Jazz fall to 16-20.
